{"about_the_game":"Sky Mad is a phenomenal futuristic jet fighter game that has flight simulation style flying based on real aircraft physics.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe objective is to complete stages, and as you complete stages it gets harder but newer and better fighters get unlocked.<br />\r\nYou can complete stages by either racing and finishing in first place or by destroying all the other jets.<br />\r\nSome stages are easier to complete by racing and others are easier to complete by destroying, you have to choose what to do with each stage.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn the demo version only the introductory stage (stage 1) is available to play and no locked fighters get unlocked.<br />\r\nIn the full version a new fighter gets unlocked every 2 stages completed and there is a total of 12 stages. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nDo you think you have what it takes to be the ultimate jet pilot till the end?<br />\r\nFlying can be hard and it may require some real aerial skills to make it through the stages.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGood luck!","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2700280?t=1715696246","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700280/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1715696246","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700280/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1715696246","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700280/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1715696246","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2719570,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"Sky Mad is a phenomenal futuristic jet fighter game that has flight simulation style flying based on real aircraft physics.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe objective is to complete stages, and as you complete stages it gets harder b